each R, R', and R" is independently selected from the group consisting of hydrogen, alkyl, alkenyl, alkynyl, and carbocyclyl;

wherein each R, R', and R" optionally is substituted with one or more substituents selected from the group consisting of alkyl, alkenyl, alkynyl, hydroxyl, alkoxy, and carbocyclyl;
B is a divalent fragment composed of one or more moieties selected from the group consisting of alkylene, alkenylene, alkynylene, (-CH2-carbocyclyl-CH2-)n, and polysiloxyl;

wherein alkylene, alkenylene, and alkynylene optionally contain one or more heteroatoms selected from the group consisting of O, N, S or Si;

