In one embodiment, a dicationic liquid salt of Formula (III) is provided, wherein

each R, R' and R" is independently selected from the group consisting of hydrogen, propyl, butyl, cyclohexanyl and phenyl;

X and Y are independently selected from the group consisting of ammonium and phosphonium;

