In another embodiment, a dicationic liquid salt of Formula (III) is provided, wherein

each R is independently selected from the group consisting of hydrogen, propyl, butyl, cyclohexanyl and phenyl;

each R' is hydrogen or phenyl;

each R" is hydrogen or 2-methoxyphenyl; and

X and Y are both phosphonium.

